Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
Prominently located along the Magnificent Mile, 737 North Michigan is only steps from distinguished hotels, award-winning restaurants, world-famous stores, luxury spas, health and fitness facilities and the area’s expanding medical campus.
737 North Michigan’s desirable location is easily accessible and provides its tenant’s employees and guests with convenient commute options. Vehicular traffic benefits from the building’s 435 car underground parking garage as well as easy access to and from I-90/94 and Lake Shore Drive. Numerous CTA bus routes along Michigan Avenue and the CTA Red Line stop on Chicago Avenue, make traveling to and from 737 North Michigan a breeze with public transportation as well.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Welcome to 737 North Michigan, a prestigious corporate environment, exemplifying style and sophistication. Designed by Skidmore Owings and Merrill with a uniquely curved exterior, 737 North Michigan is an eye-catching architectural addition to the Magnificent Mile in Chicago. With beautiful clad granite panels that taper as they ascend and floor to ceiling windows providing dramatic city views the structural design is both stunning and brilliant.
 

Consisting of 335,000 square feet of Class A office space, Neiman Marcus, luxury condominiums and a 435 car underground parking facility, 737 North Michigan caters to a diverse, high-profile audience. A recently renovated artistically inspired lobby with striking limestone floors, handsome eucalyptus wood veneered panels, and skillfully designed energy efficient lighting provides a welcoming arrival for office tenants and visitors. Superior access to distinguished hotels, luxurious spas, award-winning restaurants, and world famous stores and healthcare facilities offer convenience and office elegance on the Avenue.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
At the center of River North, one of Chicago’s most vibrant neighborhoods, 353 North Clark introduces a new paradigm for contemporary business: an impeccable office building that is designed for work and located for life.

With over 100 restaurants, numerous shops, hotels, galleries and entertainment venues within walking distance, as well as close proximity to downtown’s financial district, tenants benefit from this strategic location, ideally situated for business success.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Rising 45 stories in an astounding yet elegant composition of articulated glass and steel, 353 North Clark defines a new standard of excellence in Chicago's business landscape. The singular office building offers an unprecedented combination of Class A+ office and retail space, immediate access to the bustling River North neighborhood, and a dedicated level of service unseen in today's office environments.

The Platinum Advantage is the experience and extraordinary level of service and amenities available exclusively to our tenants.

The services offered rivals those of luxury hotels and includes:
complimentary concierge
on-site restaurants, food service and customized catering
a premier full-service health club
a dedicated commuter transport service
underground private valet parking
ample secured bike storage
a reliable messenger center
a state-of-the-art conference center
professional cobbler services
Delivered by experienced, highly trained team of managers and specialists who provide personalized services for each tenant, The Platinum Advantage elevates the working experience, making it more convenient, productive and rewarding.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: 350 North Orleans is located in the lively River North neighborhood, where work, play, fitness, lodging, and entertainment live side-by-side. Steps from the transit in a downtown full of the best restaurants, bars, hotels, and shopping Chicago has to offer; you’ll find yourself in a vibrant, creative neighborhood that begins and ends at 350 North Orleans.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Sitting along the North bank of the Chicago River, 350 North Orleans brings the best block of big floor office space, right to the heart of downtown. Providing tenants with brand new amenity spaces, large floorplates, and abundant natural light, 350 North Orleans delivers the freedom to design workspaces that drive innovation. The building blends the desirability of an authentic converted warehouse with the modernized comforts of a new office building – driving a winning formula for talent attraction and retention.

Amenities: 350 North Orleans hosts a brand new lounge and event space, stunning roof deck, and a state-of-the-art fitness center. Additionally, the building includes banking, bicycle storage, conferencing facility, security system and provides direct access to specialty shops, dining, and entertainment, via the second story pedestrian bridge.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
939 North Ave is exceptionally located at the corner of North
and Sheffield in the expanding North Avenue and
Clybourn corridor area. Superb access to downtown Chicago (3 miles),
the CTA red line (one block) and the Kennedy expressway (one mile).

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
939 North Ave offers a dramatic four-story lobby surrounded by glass panels and stainless steel accents. Committed to sustainability practices for greater energy efficiency, the high quality design, and onsite amenities set the building apart from any other. 

Building amenities include: 9'-10' finished ceilings, independent tenant HVAC availability, onsite restaurants, spa and fitness center, banking/ATM, and 24/7 manned security with card-key access. Covered parking is also available. Signage opportunity.
